casebody.data:
No. 636. W. Kelsey Kurtz, Petitioner, v. Arthur K. Brown, Surviving Receiver, etc. April 8, 1907. Mr. Rudolph M. Schick for petitioner. Mr. Reynolds D. Brown, Mr. Malcolm Lloyd, Jr., and Mr. Charles H. Burr for respondent.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Third. Circuit denied.
